    "Description": "Citizens for Prosperity recently reported to us that one of their scouts was injured by kopions during a routine exploration mission. According to them, this isn't the first time this particular pack has posed a problem, so they've requested our services to clear out the area. The report shows they were last seen at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.\n\nThis behavior is typical of kopions looking to expand their territory, so it is highly likely that you will be dealing with more kopions than initially observed. Caution is advised. \n\nBest,\n\nWanda Werkheiser\nContract Manager\nHighpoint Wilderness Specialists",
